      "role": "user",
      "content": "you mentioned \"fringe groups\" argue for biological definitions... isn't it true that there's actually a huge debate in the public and even in some medical circles about how much weight biological sex should have in these discussions? it feels like a lot more than just \"fringe\" people are talking about it.",
